	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> "For Miyazya.  has the name ወልደ ሰንባት, written into the blank, written in\n                           a different hand.  has a note of\n                           ownership in a different hand: This book belongs to the church, ዋሻ ሚካኤል during the time of Emperor Menilek\n                           (1868–1913) and Governor (Ras) Hailu (1858–1950), and Qängazmač Alemu,\n                           and church manager ቄሰ ገበዝ ተገኝ, and\n                           Märigeta ዛይህመ, church scholar, in the\n                           year of Evangelist Saint John, it was purchased. ቄሰ ገበዝ ተገኝ, whose baptismal name is ወልደ ተንሣኤ, is the one bought it as the property of the\n                           church ዋሻ ሚካኤል" ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P57_has_number_of_parts> 0 .
